{"id":606,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":606,"title":"Psalm 109","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 109"],[".studySummary",["i","David speaks of the cursings due to the wicked and deceitful—He prays that his enemies will be confounded."]],[".intro","To the chief Musician, A Psalm of David."]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.1","order":"02.20.109.39660"},["b","1"],"Hold not thy peace, O God of my praise;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.2","order":"02.20.109.39661"},["b","2"],"For the mouth of the wicked and the mouth of the deceitful are opened against me: they have spoken against me with a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lying"],"tongue."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.3","order":"02.20.109.39662"},["b","3"],"They compassed me about also with words of hatred; and fought against me without a cause."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.4","order":"02.20.109.39663"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"For"],"my love they are my adversaries: but I",["i","give myself unto"],"prayer."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.5","order":"02.20.109.39664"},["b","5"],"And they have rewarded me evil for good, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"hatred"],"for my love."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.6","order":"02.20.109.39665"},["b","6"],"Set thou a wicked man over him: and let",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Satan"],"stand at his right hand."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.7","order":"02.20.109.39666"},["b","7"],"When he shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"judged"],", let him be condemned: and let his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"prayer"],"become sin."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.8","order":"02.20.109.39667"},["b","8"],"Let his days be few;",["i","and"],"let another take his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"office"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.9","order":"02.20.109.39668"},["b","9"],"Let his children be fatherless, and his wife a widow."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.10","order":"02.20.109.39669"},["b","10"],"Let his children be continually vagabonds, and beg: let them seek",["i","their bread"],"also out of their desolate places."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.11","order":"02.20.109.39670"},["b","11"],"Let the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"extortioner catch"],"all that he hath; and let the strangers spoil his labour."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.12","order":"02.20.109.39671"},["b","12"],"Let there be none to extend mercy unto him: neither let there be any to favour his fatherless children."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.13","order":"02.20.109.39672"},["b","13"],"Let his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"posterity"],"be cut off;",["i","and"],"in the generation following let their name be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"blotted out"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.14","order":"02.20.109.39673"},["b","14"],"Let the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"iniquity"],"of his fathers be remembered with the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and let not the sin of his mother be blotted out."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.15","order":"02.20.109.39674"},["b","15"],"Let them be before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"continually, that he may cut off the memory of them from the earth."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.16","order":"02.20.109.39675"},["b","16"],"Because that he remembered not to shew mercy, but persecuted the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"poor"],"and needy man, that he might even slay the broken in heart."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.17","order":"02.20.109.39676"},["b","17"],"As he loved cursing, so let it come unto him: as he delighted not in blessing, so let it be far from him."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.18","order":"02.20.109.39677"},["b","18"],"As he clothed himself with cursing like as with his garment, so let it come into his bowels like water, and like oil into his bones."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.19","order":"02.20.109.39678"},["b","19"],"Let it be unto him as the garment",["i","which"],"covereth him, and for a girdle wherewith he is girded continually."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.20","order":"02.20.109.39679"},["b","20"],["i","Let"],"this",["i","be"],"the reward of mine adversaries from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and of them that speak evil against my soul."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.21","order":"02.20.109.39680"},["b","21"],"But do thou for me, O",["span.smallCaps","God"],"the Lord, for thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"name’s"],"sake: because thy mercy",["i","is"],"good, deliver thou me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.22","order":"02.20.109.39681"},["b","22"],"For I",["i","am"],"poor and needy, and my heart is wounded within me."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.23","order":"02.20.109.39682"},["b","23"],"I am gone like the shadow when it declineth: I am tossed up and down as the locust."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.24","order":"02.20.109.39683"},["b","24"],"My knees are weak through fasting; and my flesh faileth of fatness."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.25","order":"02.20.109.39684"},["b","25"],"I became also a reproach unto them:",["i","when"],"they looked upon me they shaked their heads."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.26","order":"02.20.109.39685"},["b","26"],"Help me, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God: O save me according to thy mercy:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.27","order":"02.20.109.39686"},["b","27"],"That they may know that this",["i","is"],"thy hand;",["i","that"],"thou,",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", hast done it."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.28","order":"02.20.109.39687"},["b","28"],"Let them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"curse"],", but bless thou: when they arise, let them be ashamed; but let thy servant rejoice."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.29","order":"02.20.109.39688"},["b","29"],"Let mine adversaries be clothed with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"shame"],", and let them cover themselves with their own confusion, as with a mantle."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.30","order":"02.20.109.39689"},["b","30"],"I will greatly praise the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with my mouth; yea, I will praise him among the multitude."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.31","order":"02.20.109.39690"},["b","31"],"For he shall stand at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"right hand"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"poor"],", to save",["i","him"],"from those that condemn his soul."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.2a","order":"02.20.109.39691"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.30.29-30"},"D&C 109:30 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.4a","order":"02.20.109.39693"},["b","4a"],["span.small","JST"],"Ps. 109:4",["i","And, notwithstanding"],"my love, they are my adversaries;",["i","yet"],"I",["i","will continue in"],"prayer",["i","for them."]],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.5a","order":"02.20.109.39695"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.15"},"1 Jn. 3:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.6a","order":"02.20.109.39697"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"an adversary, accuser.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/3.1"},"Zech. 3:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.7a","order":"02.20.109.39699"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/2.13"},"James 2:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/8.25"},"Hel. 8:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.23.20-23"},"D&C 10:23 (20–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.24.23-25"},"121:24 (23–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.7b","order":"02.20.109.39701"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.9"},"Prov. 28:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.25.24-25"},"Mosiah 11:25 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.8a","order":"02.20.109.39703"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.20.16-20"},"Acts 1:20 (16–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.11a","order":"02.20.109.39705"},["b","11a"],["span.small","OR"],"creditors seize."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.13a","order":"02.20.109.39707"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/21.10.10-11"},"Ps. 21:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/37.28"},"37:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.20"},"Isa. 14:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.20"},"2 Ne. 24:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.15.13-15"},"D&C 121:15 (13–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.13b","order":"02.20.109.39709"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.36"},"Mosiah 26:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.57.56-58"},"Alma 5:57 (56–58)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.83"},"D&C 20:83"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.14a","order":"02.20.109.39711"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.5"},"Ex. 20:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.16a","order":"02.20.109.39713"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/86.1"},"Ps. 86:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.55.54-56"},"Alma 5:55 (54–56)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.39.39-40"},"Hel. 6:39 (39–40)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.16"},"D&C 56:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.21a","order":"02.20.109.39715"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/23.3"},"Ps. 23:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/25.11"},"25:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/31.3"},"31:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.28a","order":"02.20.109.39717"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.29a","order":"02.20.109.39719"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/71.13"},"Ps. 71:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.31a","order":"02.20.109.39721"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/16.8"},"Ps. 16:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.31b","order":"02.20.109.39723"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.18.15-18"},"D&C 56:18 (15–18)"],"."]]}
